# tests/

Comprehensive BATS test suite for Intent CLI covering unit and integration scenarios. Tests include command routing, project operations, rule library validation, critic infrastructure, and end-to-end workflows. Suite runs via run_tests.sh with configurable test paths and colored output.

## Dirs

- `fixtures/` -- Test fixtures and sample files
- `integration/` -- End-to-end workflow and integration tests
- `lib/` -- BATS helper libraries and utilities
- `unit/` -- Unit tests for all CLI commands and subsystems

## Files

- `README.md` -- Test suite documentation and prerequisites
- `run_tests.sh` -- Main test runner with Bats configuration and colored output
